<div class="box">
  <h1>滕州一中校友会 API 参考</h1>
  <p>下面是简单的 API 路由列表, 具体请参考源代码 <a href="https://github.com/imWildCat/tzyz/blob/master/app/api/v1/tzyz_api_v1.rb" target="_blank">api.rb</a></p>
  <table class="table">
    <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Method</th>
      <th>URL</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <% TzyzApiV1.routes.each do |route| %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= route.route_method %></td>
          <% route_path = route.route_path.gsub("(.:format)",".json") %>
          <td><%= route.route_path.gsub("(.:format)",".json") %></td>
        </tr>
    <% end %>
    </table>
</div>